Xitrum (XT) is a super fast web server and web framework on top of Netty.

+-----------------+
|    Your app     |
+-----------------+
|       XT        |
| +-------------+ |
| |  Framework  | |
| +-------------+ |
| | Middlewares | |
| +-------------+ |
| |   Server    | |
| +-------------+ |
+-----------------+
|      Netty      |
+-----------------+

Things in XT are tightly coupled for speed.
